Package gobblin.compaction.hivebasedconstructs

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CompactionLauncherWriter
    DataWriter that launches an MRCompactor job given an MRCompactionEntity specifying config for compaction Delta field is passed using ConfBasedDeltaFieldProvider
    CompactionLauncherWriterBuilder
    DataWriterBuilder for CompactionLauncherWriter
    HiveMetadataForCompactionExtractor
    Extractor that extracts primary key field name, delta field name, and location from hive metastore and creates an MRCompactionEntity
    HiveMetadataForCompactionExtractorFactory
    Factory for HiveMetadataForCompactionExtractor
    MRCompactionEntity
    Entity that stores information required for launching an MRCompactor job MRCompactionEntity.primaryKeyList: Comma delimited list of fields to use as primary key MRCompactionEntity.deltaList: Comma delimited list of fields to use as deltaList MRCompactionEntity.dataFilesPath: Location of files associated with table MRCompactionEntity.props: Other properties to be passed to MRCompactor
